Package: ofono-config-ril-binder
Architecture: all
Pre-Depends: ofono
Depends: ${misc:Depends},
         ofono-ril-binder-plugin
Description: ofono configuration for devices using binder as transport
 This package contains the ofono configuration for devices using
 binder as transport.

Package: ofono-config-ril-binder-dual-sim
Architecture: all
Depends: ofono-config-ril-binder (= ${binary:Version})
Conflicts: ofono-config-ril-binder-single-sim-sim2
Description: ofono configuration for devices using binder as transport (dual sim addon)
 This package contains the ofono configuration for devices using
 binder as transport.
 .
 This package adds support for dual sim devices.

Package: ofono-config-ril-binder-single-sim-sim2
Architecture: all
Depends: ofono-config-ril-binder (= ${binary:Version})
Conflicts: ofono-config-ril-binder-dual-sim
Description: ofono configuration for devices using binder as transport (dual sim addon, SIM2-only)
 This package contains the ofono configuration for devices using
 binder as transport.
 .
 This package adds support for dual sim devices, but forces only SIM2 to be used.
